{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji31.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给王首道的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给王首道的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年11月21日）首道同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请酌予此人以生活上的照顾。据周世钊校长说，此人一生办教育（曾在第一师范当过教员），似无劣迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿一日[1]王首道，当时任湖南省人民政府主席。[2]指李醒安，原名李廉翘，曾在湖南省立第一师范学校当教员。[3]周世钊，当时任湖南省立第一师范学校校长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":11,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":86,"page_end":86},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}